headline: Tractor Supply Raises Over $1 Million for 2025 FFA Future Leaders Scholarships
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., December 02, 2024--Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), the largest rural lifestyle retailer in the United States, announced today it has raised more than $1 million to support the Tractor Supply FFA Future Leaders Scholarship fund. With this achievement, the annual fundraiser has generated a total of more than $3 million over three years.
